<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Aw Kalvari!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw kalvari tang chung achun,
 Ka Lalpa A kiko;
 Jerusalem, Kanaan gam cheng cheng,
 Na lal uh hi lo maw? (2)

[V2]
 Aw ka gen thei puoi, aw ka sut thiem puoi,
 Ei hehpih a mak na e!
 Thukna,thukna, ka gen thei puoi,
 Ei hehpih a mak na e!

[V3]
 2. Puonzak lopi a kithek a,
 Suongpi hung khi phel chu;
 Hehpihna Pathien lunggil achun,
 Bangtin ana ta dem? (2)

[V4]
 3. Khawvel cheng a hung thim ta a,
 Lei a hung kiling a;
 Lau in khawvel a taimang ta a,
 Mi thiengtho a tho tau. (2)</lyrics>
<author>Patea</author>
<hymn_number>61</hymn_number>
</song>